<a:aa_exclemation:721133798024020038> **Rules** <a:aa_exclemation:721133798024020038>
```Please make sure you have read and accepted the xmas game order info in the game order channel```

<a:bb_pink_arrow:721937416411152394> **How to Order**

`giraffa order` :: displays the list of available games
The  first number per row is the ID that will be used for ordering.

`giraffa orderadd <ID>` :: this will add the game to your order

`giraffa orderremove <ID>` :: will remove the game from you order

`giraffa myorder` :: this will show you a summary of your order
